<item>
            <title>[FELIX-1610] OBR repository update check is hard-coded at 7 days</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1610</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;OBR repository provided hard codes update check as 7 days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It makes no account of file: URLs, so once it has copied a file: URL to its cache, it won&apos;t update it for 7 days.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12435945">FELIX-1610</key>
            <summary>OBR repository update check is hard-coded at 7 days</summary>
